    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dumbz Snake</strong> is an action game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight on a dynamic desert island</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move strategically around this sunny desert island, but be careful: the sea level is rising steadily. And earthworms don't like the sea...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126890/extras/e98d80ad101d5806a5db1549958f1471.avif?t=1750062564\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126890/extras_big/e98d80ad101d5806a5db1549958f1471.avif?t=1750062564 width=800 height=326 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Use your spells to fight</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive other players' attacks, and use strategy to attack them with your spells!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126890/extras/b65fdc420820ec1592855393a4540810.avif?t=1750062564\" width=800 height=330 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Grow your Snake by absorbing orbs</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Glowing orbs of different colors appear every 30-45 seconds. Eating orbs will allow you to increase the length and size of your Snake to gain an advantage!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126890/extras/fb078cb308885d76089a57d1910d4637.avif?t=1750062564\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126890/extras_big/fb078cb308885d76089a57d1910d4637.avif?t=1750062564 width=800 height=414 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
